{"tid":2400351,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭松泰屌9人唔比養狗","createTime":"2021-02-09T01:31:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-09T06:02:58.000Z","uid":189799,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a1d59a714fe08fd6dabcfce4a98499b453603551","tid":2400351,"uid":189799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T01:31:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d18pTPu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd18pTPu.jpg&h=d03a6af9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一城議員回應<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KB00r9H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKB00r9H.jpg&h=30fbdb48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n基本上，兩個人各執一詞。<br />\n但鄭松泰係【有一位朋友哭訴】，咁可信性就自己判斷啦。<br />\n<br />\n不過，第一城公契寫明唔比養狗，隻眼開隻眼閉係人情，捉9你係道理。<br />\n<br />\n買樓前好應該了解清楚屋苑可否養狗，明知唔比養而又買樓，咁好明顯係業主責任。想養狗咪買其他屋苑囉。<br />\n<br />\n所以強行執行之說根本就係強詞奪理，惡人先告狀。<br />\n<br />\n跟蹤拍照又係on9。咁管理處要叫你唔好養，咁梗係要影相做證據先同你講架啦。無證據人地點會理9你呀。<br />\n<br />\n最後，鄭松泰我屌你老味"},{"pid":"3e132c95ee7924d607aa542297e35a88e02202ab","tid":2400351,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T01:32:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94d5b03787c50894bbcd216d5daca116abbcadee","tid":2400351,"uid":344173,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T01:36:56.000Z","msg":"私人樓宇好似不嬲都唔俾養狗（當然可能其他私人地方容許呢一樣野）不過就算話唔俾其實大多數都係隻眼開隻眼閉居多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好少可特登捉<br />\n熱狗好鍾意spin去人權自由，再藉此話所謂嘅黃絲「endorse 政權」<br />\n之前有區議員跟進非法賽車又係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8a278405bb4caef15c0b09817b9af254a32c270","tid":2400351,"uid":189799,"lik